window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I never thought I’d see her again - let alone find her in the same spot I left her 10 years ago, teaching at the high school where we fell in love. </p> <p>I should have kept walking, but I wanted that laugh, that smile. I wanted five minutes before I got back to a life with no room for my past. </p> <p>One kiss was all I meant to take...but then her fingers were in my hair, her breath hot against my lips, and my hands...everywhere. </p> <p>Now I want more. I want her, but she only wants the guy I used to be. </p> <p>And just like the first time...I can’t stay, and she won’t leave.</p>"; 
